        <td><code>ToolProvider(builtin-coding-tools)</code></td>
        <td>Workspace file, search, patch, edit, workflow, media, shell, and command tools.</td>
        <td><code>fs.read.workspace</code>, <code>fs.write.workspace</code>, <code>process.spawn.shell</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
