  <p>
    The default TUI extension installs status segments for <code>mode</code>, <code>model</code>,
    <code>session</code>, <code>branch</code>, <code>usage</code>, <code>mcp</code>, and
    <code>runner</code>. It also installs palette sources for <code>commands</code>,
    <code>sessions</code>, <code>agents</code>, <code>models</code>, <code>modes</code>,
    <code>workflow-imports</code>, and <code>media</code>.
  </p>

